  },
  "description": {
    "en": "The twelve regular meridians (十二正經) and eight extraordinary meridians (奇經八脈) in Traditional Chinese Medicine. Herbs 'enter' specific meridians, directing their therapeutic action.",
    "zh-Hant": "中醫十二正經與奇經八脈。藥物歸經，引導藥力到達相關臟腑。"
  },
